These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, cooking, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, pilot, dancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, hip-hop, electronic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, goat, guinea-pig
1. the software-developer is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the nurse##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the software-developer##1
5. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of funk##1
7. the software-developer is the owner of the chinchilla##1
8. the fan of funk is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | chess  | rock-climbing  | puzzles | cooking |
| Job           | software-developer | nurse | dancer  | pilot  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic       | hip-hop      | blues | funk      |
| Pet           | chinchilla          | hamster     | goat    | guinea-pig     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, water, milk
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapes, asparagus, pear
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, pop, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling, skiing, rugby
1. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
2. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | water     | coffee       | hot-chocolate | milk        |
| Food          | pear     | grapes       | asparagus   | potato   |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | ambient       | punk     | hip-hop    |
| Sport         | skiing | rugby | weightlifting | cycling |

