.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, police-officer, coach, engineer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, documentary, time-travel, thriller
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, fish, hamster
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the police-officer##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the social-worker##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | cola | fanta       | iced-tea        | almond-milk        |
| Job           | police-officer   | coach | social-worker   | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | documentary    | thriller | time-travel        |
| Pet           | fish         | ferret  | hamster       | turtle         |

