.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, nurse, architect, dressmaker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, techno, classical, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: german, chinese, japanese, french
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, dog, mouse
1. the japanese is on the left of the analyst##1
2. the architect is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of techno##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the nurse##1
7. the dressmaker is on the right of the analyst##1
8. the german is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the dog is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | nurse   | analyst  | dressmaker | architect |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance       | techno       | r&b     |
| Nationality   | japanese       | french    | chinese     | german  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog | mouse     | turtle         |

