.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, paramedic, dancer, project-manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, musical, western, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, colombian, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, golf, skateboarding, parkour
1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the writer##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the colombian##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the paramedic is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | writer  | dancer    | paramedic | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | musical    | satire         | mystery    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | dutch     | colombian          | argentine      |
| Sport         | golf | swimming | parkour      | skateboarding      |

