The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, bartender, pilot, ferreterman
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, time-travel, action, epic
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, turtle, snake
 1. the person eating plum is the person watching western movies##1
 2. the person eating mango is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the project-manager is the person watching western movies##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is the person eating mango##1
 5. the person watching action movies is the ferreterman##1
 6. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 7. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the pilot is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | mango  | grapes | plum     | pumpkin |
| Job           | pilot  | ferreterman      | project-manager | bartender    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | action  | western    | epic  |
