.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, juice, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, singing, dancing
4 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, rabbit, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, helicopter, boat
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | cola | 7up     | juice    | almond-milk |
| Hobby       | puzzles | singing    | dancing | photography |
| Pet         | horse   | rabbit  | hamster        | turtle    |
| Transport   | boat   | train | motorbike    | helicopter |

